    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时间石英》的世界每一步都很重要！每个循环有10个回合可以行动，可以探索、解谜、运用过去获得的知识继续前进。这是一段有关时间的特殊冒险，你需要策略、批判性思考和时间管理。你最后能拯救时间吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每一步都很重要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《时间石英》的世界，你行动的次数有限，必须精打细算，充分利用每个循环的10个回合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/26f6db434c7937be6d3ab2e4ed55128f.poster.avif?t=1768567356\" width=666 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/26f6db434c7937be6d3ab2e4ed55128f.webm?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/26f6db434c7937be6d3ab2e4ed55128f.mp4?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时间循环</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >必须运用之前获取的关键情报，才能推进游戏进度，例如打开加密的门，进入秘密通道，得知物体的位置，还有摸索出到达目的地的最短路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/0602b96435b1a5a3ea6f51b1e74dd6b9.poster.avif?t=1768567356\" width=666 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/0602b96435b1a5a3ea6f51b1e74dd6b9.webm?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/0602b96435b1a5a3ea6f51b1e74dd6b9.mp4?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >着眼长远</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个循环都要决定该走哪条路，该拿哪件东西。你可以行动的回合有限，三思而后行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/02902ea9b96f3d94dc78ce682d9d8c4b.poster.avif?t=1768567356\" width=666 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/02902ea9b96f3d94dc78ce682d9d8c4b.webm?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/02902ea9b96f3d94dc78ce682d9d8c4b.mp4?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时空谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要洞悉这个世界的奥秘，就要破解横跨一个乃至多个循环的谜题。务必细致规划，因为不要忘了，每一个步都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/cadecf9f80e72560d66cbd5cae2ff72c.poster.avif?t=1768567356\" width=666 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/cadecf9f80e72560d66cbd5cae2ff72c.webm?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/cadecf9f80e72560d66cbd5cae2ff72c.mp4?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拯救时间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你获得的情报都有可能助你挫败莫尔萨斯的阴谋。他企图夺取时间石英，篡改历史。时间需要你，最终能获得你的拯救吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/68a175d9de03dfde25c13e926151afcd.poster.avif?t=1768567356\" width=666 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/68a175d9de03dfde25c13e926151afcd.webm?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275880/extras/68a175d9de03dfde25c13e926151afcd.mp4?t=1768567356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
